{"tid":1602383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"入黎認人呀_被捕人士關注組","createTime":"2019-09-29T11:34:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T08:38:39.000Z","uid":255826,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5f835229b1c72b7f5dc64c3b4e560e71fc1f6014","tid":1602383,"uid":255826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T11:34:55.000Z","msg":"由6月9日起，每一日被拘捕嘅數字都不斷增長。人數就有喇，但佢嘅去向同埋上庭嘅門日子要好留意新聞先睇到。我哋同大家一樣非常關心被捕人仕嘅去向，無論係前中後線、街坊、守護連儂牆，為咗大家付出過嘅義士。一個都不能少！<br />\n<br />\nMARK實日子📌📌<br />\n我哋要一齊同佢哋行落去💪🏻💪🏻💪🏻<br />\n最新消息請大家話我哋知<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家提供新聞比我哋做整合🙏🏻<br />\n<br />\n一有上庭時間就會出公告<br />\n我哋要去聲援佢哋<br />\n〔齊上齊落💪🏻〕<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求🗣<br />\n缺一不可🗣<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk&d=AXXoxpexL8qkFRpCGxAvLRPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=4aa6bc8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk</a>"},{"pid":"d1df81be16ecfa06391808b5c964cc415dd430d3","tid":1602383,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T11:41:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0d0c7a55fb775a0654f80dab91b09c21b483ecaa","tid":1602383,"uid":255826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T11:41:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"65f9b3f5851020b7526645cc8f8a10598b7d42e3","tid":1602383,"uid":255826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T11:41:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"38cbdb1598ddc53492c53752d2e927898ea41051","tid":1602383,"uid":255826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T11:41:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"35f7e1482cbaf232ebddc0da109d2daccda81906","tid":1602383,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T11:41:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ecd3a360826be8d74a87927988ae1e78e0375ac4","tid":1602383,"uid":255826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T11:44:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"378c66f66a7298fd4879a3b08422d